  "detailed_description": "<h1>WISHLIST AND FOLLOW US!</h1><p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/772730/extras/8d558fa1850ba53f5c42a1b3145b82b3.poster.avif?t=1767808613\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/772730/extras/8d558fa1850ba53f5c42a1b3145b82b3.webm?t=1767808613\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/772730/extras/8d558fa1850ba53f5c42a1b3145b82b3.mp4?t=1767808613\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>After escaping France, The Templars move to the North of Europe to help the elves against Destruction forces!<br><br>To Victory brothers!<br><br>DEUS VULT!</strong></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BECOME A WARRIOR</h2>The elves and the dark elves need to make peace, or they will face their Doomsday. <br><br>The Knight Templars are here to help them out! Find out who is behind the Orc and gobos legions!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/772730/extras/7b4dda46beeefa54c383fb0a0e0a53c2.poster.avif?t=1767808613\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/772730/extras/7b4dda46beeefa54c383fb0a0e0a53c2.webm?t=1767808613\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/772730/extras/7b4dda46beeefa54c383fb0a0e0a53c2.mp4?t=1767808613\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features In Game:</h2>* 3rd person combat experience!<br>*Skirmish fights in the North East of Europe!<br>*Fight Orcs and goblins!<br>*Fight Pagans!<br>*Rich lore and story!<br>*Many love stories and characters!<br>*Play with different characters and classes along the story!<br>*Close combat with swords, knives, blades, scythe!<br>*Range combat with crossbow, bows, grenades!<br>*Dragon boss fight!<br>*Big monster boss fights!<br>*Many fun achievements to unlock!<br>*And much more!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >What are you waiting for? if you like elves and dark elves, this game is for you! </h2>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BECOME A WARRIOR</h2>The elves and the dark elves need to make peace, or they will face their Doomsday. <br><br>The Knight Templars are here to help them out! Find out who is behind the Orc and gobos legions!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/772730/extras/7b4dda46beeefa54c383fb0a0e0a53c2.poster.avif?t=1767808613\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/772730/extras/7b4dda46beeefa54c383fb0a0e0a53c2.webm?t=1767808613\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/772730/extras/7b4dda46beeefa54c383fb0a0e0a53c2.mp4?t=1767808613\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features In Game:</h2>* 3rd person combat experience!<br>*Skirmish fights in the North East of Europe!<br>*Fight Orcs and goblins!<br>*Fight Pagans!<br>*Rich lore and story!<br>*Many love stories and characters!<br>*Play with different characters and classes along the story!<br>*Close combat with swords, knives, blades, scythe!<br>*Range combat with crossbow, bows, grenades!<br>*Dragon boss fight!<br>*Big monster boss fights!<br>*Many fun achievements to unlock!<br>*And much more!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >What are you waiting for? if you like elves and dark elves, this game is for you! </h2>",
